reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great sturdy and cute nightstand!
reviews.reviewText: Love this nightstand for my new setup! Picture quality is a little dark - but just showing how cute it looks! Picked this color because it matches well with the wooden pieces on my bed frame and also provides a nice contrast to the flooring and grey headboard in my room. Setup was easy with all parts clearly labeled. Took about 20 min to finish building the nightstand. Overall it’s very sturdy and has some weight to it so not worried about it feeling flimsy at all. Drawer slides in and out easily and I like that they made the knob match to the black (I’ve seen some where it doesn’t match and it’s weird!) the drawer is small but perfect for what I need to put inside it. I like the shelf piecing on the bottom as well - will probably put a few books or laptop there if I’m using at night. Price is also great as it includes 2 nightstands total for under $100. Also like that bottom has adjustable pieces for height slightly (in case one or 2 legs are on a rug or something and uneven height). Would highly recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Affordable pricing, sturdy and stylish
reviews.reviewText: I absolutely love the VECELO End Tables Set of 2! These nightstands have been a fantastic addition to my bedroom. The design is modern and sleek, and the vintage brown color adds a touch of elegance to the room. The drawers and shelves offer ample storage space, keeping my essentials neatly organized and easily accessible.The industrial metal frame not only looks stylish but also adds sturdiness to the tables. I appreciate the high-quality construction that ensures these nightstands will last for years to come. They are incredibly sturdy, and I have no worries about them holding up to everyday use.One of the best things about these nightstands is their affordable pricing. They provide excellent value for the money spent, giving me a high-end look without breaking the bank. The quality and features they offer at this price point are truly impressive.Assembly was a breeze! I was able to put them together without any hassle, thanks to the clear instructions and well-organized parts. It took no time at all, and I could start enjoying my new nightstands immediately.I'm impressed with the overall craftsmanship and attention to detail. These nightstands have truly elevated the look of my bedroom, creating a cozy and inviting ambiance. I highly recommend the VECELO End Tables Set of 2 to anyone looking for stylish, sturdy, and affordable nightstands that are easy to assemble. They are worth every penny and more!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy little nightstands
reviews.reviewText: The pros: they look nice and they are sturdier than you think when looking at them.The cons: They are very short and small. They look like they should be in a child’s room. I kept them because we put them together before I saw how short they are. They are lower than the top of my mattress which looks weird.Also- even though they aren’t difficult to assemble, it was time consuming. I have a hard time believing anyone could assemble two of these in under a couple of hours.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 17, 2023
reviews.reviewText: It’s a very pretty nightstand. Well made and easy to assemble. All the parts were included. Instructions are clear and easy to follow. The mistake I made was not paying attention to the size of these tables. Next to my bed they look extremely tiny. When I placed them next to my bed I couldn’t help busting out laughing. It was hilarious. I did get them while they were on sale. They would probably be better suited as end table next to a small loveseat.
